                	<li><a href="#1" class="a1">查看车辆各类证件<span></span></a></li>
                	<li><a href="#2" class="a2 current">查看车辆变更记录<span></span></a></li>
                	<li><a href="#3" class="a3">辨别营运车辆<span></span></a></li>
                	<li><a href="#4" class="a4">查看车辆保险信息到期时间<span></span></a></li>
                	<li><a href="#5" class="a5">查看年检到期时间<span></span></a></li>
                	<li><a href="#6" class="a6">欠费以及违章车查询<span></span></a></li>
                	<li><a href="#7" class="a7">车况检测<span></span></a></li>
                	<li><a href="#8" class="a8">钱款只交付给谁<span></span></a></li>
                	<li><a href="#9" class="a9">及时过户<span></span></a></li>
                	<li><a href="#10" class="a10">转籍车辆需符合当地落户标<span></span></a></li>
                </ul>
